ScriptBlocks.ScriptBlock: Sub FillComboList(Combobox)[vbCrLf]'Erzeugen der Einträge in der Combobox-Liste[vbCrLf]' Input : Combobox-> Combobox-Objekt[vbCrLf]' Beispiel :[vbCrLf]' Combobox.Clear [vbCrLf]' Combobox.AddItem(<Beliebiger Text>) [vbCrLf] Combobox.Clear[vbCrLf][vbCrLf][vbCrLf][vbCrLf] Set CDevRoot = Project.gethierarchyobjectbyname(Project.cdevices,CDevRootFullName )[vbCrLf] If Not CDevRoot Is Nothing Then[vbCrLf] If Trim(cstr(EmptyValueText)) <> "" Then[vbCrLf] combobox.additem cstr(EmptyValueText)[vbCrLf] End If[vbCrLf][vbCrLf] For i = 1 To CDevRoot.CDevices.Count[vbCrLf] combobox.additem cdevroot.cdevices.Item(i).Description[vbCrLf] Next[vbCrLf][vbCrLf] End If[vbCrLf]End Sub

' Values setzen:[vbCrLf]' Hier den Element-Namen und den[vbCrLf]' RootKnoten für die Stammobjekteauswahl eintragen[vbCrLf][vbCrLf][vbCrLf]' CDeviceFullName für den Knoten, [vbCrLf]' unter dem sich die auszuwählenden CDevice-Objekte befinden [vbCrLf]CDevRootFullname = "@System|@D|@GRAFICS|@LAYERS|RI2" [vbCrLf][vbCrLf]' String, der ausgeben wird, um <keine Auswahl> [vbCrLf]' auszuwählen[vbCrLf]' (Wird nur angezeigt, wenn <> "" ) [vbCrLf]If Not Project.CurrentLanguage Is Nothing Then[vbCrLf] If Project.CurrentLanguage.Name = "1" Then[vbCrLf] EmptyValuetext = "Keine"[vbCrLf] Else [vbCrLf] EmptyValuetext = "None"[vbCrLf] End If[vbCrLf]Else[vbCrLf] EmptyValuetext = "Keine"[vbCrLf]End If

Sub SetScriptValue (value)[vbCrLf]'Wird durchgeführt beim Setzen des Spezifikationswertes[vbCrLf]' Input : Value -> Spezifikationswert[vbCrLf] [vbCrLf] If value <> "" Then[vbCrLf] lib.device.SetSubObjbyCDevDesc GetSpecOwner() ,cstr(CDevRootFullname ),cstr(value)[vbCrLf] End If[vbCrLf][vbCrLf]End Sub

Sub FillComboList(Combobox)[vbCrLf]'Erzeugen der Einträge in der Combobox-Liste[vbCrLf]' Input : Combobox-> Combobox-Objekt[vbCrLf]' Beispiel :[vbCrLf]' Combobox.Clear [vbCrLf]' Combobox.AddItem(<Beliebiger Text>)[vbCrLf][vbCrLf]' BaseCDevFullName = "@F|A1|01"[vbCrLf]' BaseCDevFullName = "@03|BAS|IEC|@F|01"[vbCrLf] BaseCDevFullName = GetCDevFunctionsSystemFullname[vbCrLf][vbCrLf] Combobox.Clear[vbCrLf] [vbCrLf] Combobox.AddItem "0"[vbCrLf] [vbCrLf] Set Dev = GetSpecOwner()[vbCrLf] If Dev.SystemTypeName = "Device" Then[vbCrLf][vbCrLf] Set BaseCDev = Project.GetHierarchyObjectByName(Project.CDevices,BaseCDevFullName)[vbCrLf][vbCrLf] If BaseCDev Is Nothing Then[vbCrLf] Exit Sub[vbCrLf] End If [vbCrLf] [vbCrLf] Set devCDev = dev.cdevice[vbCrLf] If devCDev.iselement Then[vbCrLf] Set devCDev = devCDev.CDevice[vbCrLf] End If[vbCrLf] [vbCrLf] [vbCrLf] 'das passende Objekt aus der zweistufigen Struktur suchen[vbCrLf] If devCDev.owner Is BaseCDev Then[vbCrLf] Set CDevLevel1 = devCDev [vbCrLf] ElseIf devCDev.owner.owner Is BaseCDev Then[vbCrLf] Set CDevLevel1 = devCDev.owner[vbCrLf] Else[vbCrLf] Exit Sub[vbCrLf] End If [vbCrLf] [vbCrLf] For i = 1 To CDevLevel1.CDevices.Count[vbCrLf] Combobox.AddItem CStr(i)[vbCrLf] Next[vbCrLf] [vbCrLf] [vbCrLf] End If[vbCrLf] [vbCrLf]End Sub[vbCrLf][vbCrLf]Function GetCDevFunctionsSystemFullname[vbCrLf] Set atrNorm= Project.Workset.GetCurrentProject.spec("COM010.COM4002")[vbCrLf] If atrNorm Is Nothing Then Exit Function[vbCrLf] Set MainCDevPositions = atrNorm.LinkObject[vbCrLf] If MainCDevPositions Is Nothing Then Exit Function[vbCrLf] GetCDevFunctionsSystemFullname=MainCDevPositions.SystemFullName[vbCrLf]End Function
